{"tid":1296263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住麥當勞","createTime":"2019-07-08T10:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:10:00.000Z","uid":10905,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"897e01ff1894dd24c80a6108cd8860085aaa3341","tid":1296263,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩我拎餐果陣唔小心倒瀉左成杯可樂落你地張枱度<br />\n仲淋濕曬d調味料呀紙巾呀果d搞到全部都唔用得<br />\n又唔執得餐住要清左先仲要痴立立<br />\n<br />\n真係好對唔住呀我一諗起琴日有警察懷疑係麥當勞打人又拎住個盾推推撞撞我緊張得濟控制唔到自己先會推左杯野警黎<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地會唔會要我賠番d調味料呢<br />\n不過都冇嫁啦你地都冇cam既有都係壞左<br />\n<br />\n真係好對唔住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c451b0e1b0067ebffeccef28ed98e304f6f1c6b4","tid":1296263,"uid":111316,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"你玩9班老麥員工有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多後生細仔番part time<br />\n一陣搞著自己人"},{"pid":"9288c46c16bcd34349f295c70a2fa7f0d180a345","tid":1296263,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c451b0e1b0067ebffeccef28ed98e304f6f1c6b4","tid":1296263,"uid":111316,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"你玩9班老麥員工有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多後生細仔番part time<br />\n一陣搞著自己人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"咁係咪應該去總部office倒瀉野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ff5553b2997d07e033e9a25f2c0e26e9471d71","tid":1296263,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c451b0e1b0067ebffeccef28ed98e304f6f1c6b4","tid":1296263,"uid":111316,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"你玩9班老麥員工有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多後生細仔番part time<br />\n一陣搞著自己人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"就係想返工基層果班選擇更好工作，淨番果D高層死守！"},{"pid":"9d369d74ad899a1bf6a4d2