_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Facebook page</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JiJqJK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JiJqJK&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=f8f5cf13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JiJqJK</a><br />\n<br />\n補充表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/iRy1HizFPhpaGNt38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FiRy1HizFPhpaGNt38&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=7665f99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/iRy1HizFPhpaGNt38</a>"},{"pid":"46f9be74cec015b344de8c3bbbb31bab8de77f12","tid":1296263,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c451b0e1b0067ebffeccef28ed98e304f6f1c6b4","tid":1296263,"uid":111316,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"你玩9班老麥員工有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多後生細仔番part time<br />\n一陣搞著自己人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"對唔住呀<br />\n岩岩就係搞到執餐果個位執唔到<br />\n所以收銀停一停先<br />\n搞到好多人都買唔到<br />\n有d嫌排得太耐走左<br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀搞到你地做少左生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩我朋友同我講番老麥絕大部分都係計時薪<br />\n因為我佢地成條鏈停曬手冇野做當休息下<br />\n我都冇咁內疚"},{"pid":"7480cdcbcbbd51b5674e0e88ef1f2ac0a82563b3","tid":1296263,"uid":119026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"cctv唔係話睇就比你睇得嫁啦. <br />\n如果講一句，就比人睇。咁真係會侵犯私隱.<br />\n<br />\n如果用呢個理由罷食，我覺得都好難說服人.<br />\n<br />\n如果你話比人打個位 需要拎證據上法庭，而麥當勞唔比. 咁呢個理由就唔同啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣我支持罷食! <br />\n<br />\nbtw, <br />\n不過，我諗都有唔少人都靠食麥記儲錢"}]}